EventItemTitle:
Tour - Grand Central Partnership, New York City

M E M O R A N D U M

October 20, 1999

TO: ALL COUNCIL MEMBERS
RE: TOUR/MEETING BY THE COMMITTEE ON ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT

Please be advised that all Council Members are invited to attend a tour/meeting of the Grand Central Partnership, located at 122 East 42nd St. (Lexington Avenue), New York N.Y.

The tour will be on Thursday, October 28, 1999 beginning at 12:00 P.M. and will end at approximately 2:00 P.M. A van will be leaving City Hall at 11:30 A.M. and will return at approximately 2:30 P.M.

Council Members interested in attending should call Todd Turner at 788-9073 no later than Wednesday, October 27, 1999.

Jerome X. O'Donovan, Chairperson 
Committee on Economic Development
EventItemMatterName: Tour - Grand Central Partnership, New York City
